{"id":4260,"date":"2026-01-04T08:58:26","date_gmt":"2026-01-04T03:28:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/?page_id=4260"},"modified":"2026-01-04T09:25:43","modified_gmt":"2026-01-04T03:55:43","slug":"astonishing-science-behind-sound-which-heals-body-empowers-to-create-universe-elevates-to-spiritual-realm","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/seminars\/2025\/japan\/mysteries-of-sound\/","title":{"rendered":"Astonishing Science behind Sound\u00a0\u2013 which heals\u00a0body, empowers to create\u00a0universe\u00a0&amp; elevates to Spiritual\u00a0realm !\u00a0"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Sound Vibration &amp; Mantra by HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj on 09 Nov 2025\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/QzkohheTP0Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Seminar on\u00a0Mysteries of Sound\u00a0| HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj | ISKCON Japan | November 9,\u00a02025\u00a0|<\/strong>\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Hare&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Hare&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Jaya&nbsp;Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;Jaya&nbsp;Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;Jaya&nbsp;Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj:<\/strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So, in Lord Caitanya&#8217;s movement, Nama\u00a0Sankirtan\u00a0is considered the main process for spiritual advancement. And many people will question why this sound is so important? If we examine\u00a0the Vedic\u00a0literature,\u00a0we&#8217;ll\u00a0see that sound is\u00a0very important.\u00a0Apart from\u00a0what&#8217;s\u00a0stated\u00a0in the Vedic\u00a0literatures, we find that sound is\u00a0very important\u00a0in this material world. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"551\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-96-1024x551.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4377\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-96-1024x551.png 1024w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-96-300x161.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-96-768x413.png 768w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-96-1536x826.png 1536w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-96.png 1597w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So sound, of course, is\u00a0vibration\u00a0of molecules.\u00a0And if they vibrate different frequencies, we get different sounds. But if we examine matter,\u00a0we&#8217;ll\u00a0find that we have these little particles called atoms and whatever, and everything is vibrating. We cannot hear\u00a0sound\u00a0of these atoms vibrating, but\u00a0actually [Laughs]\u00a0they are vibrating.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"504\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-47.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4316\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-47.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-47-300x168.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-47-768x430.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;everything has its frequency of vibration. And we take molecules and bind them&nbsp;together,&nbsp;the molecules are also vibrating.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"504\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-48.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4317\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-48.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-48-300x168.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-48-768x430.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And if we get the molecules together and we form a human body,&nbsp;human&nbsp;body is also vibrating.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in the 1900s, some curious scientists began to measure the vibrations of the different organs&nbsp;of&nbsp;your body.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"508\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-49.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4318\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-49.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-49-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-49-768x433.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And they found that each organ had&nbsp;a very specific&nbsp;vibration if it was healthy. And they also found if the organ is unhealthy and&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;going through&nbsp;wrong vibration, if we put the right vibration back into the organ, then the organ heals itself.&nbsp;So, this is quite a different concept of health compared to most conventional&nbsp;medicine.&nbsp;In the modern world,&nbsp;generally we&nbsp;depend on pills and surgical&nbsp;knife&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;But these scientists found that vibration was&nbsp;very important&nbsp;for the health of&nbsp;an&nbsp;organ.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"508\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-50.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4319\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-50.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-50-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-50-768x433.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;since that time, many scientists have been investigating this idea of vibration as a cure.&nbsp;And with the advent of computers and more detailed measurements, then this type of detection of disease and also cure of diseases has become very advanced.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"499\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-51.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4320\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-51.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-51-300x166.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-51-768x425.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;without cutting up your body or even taking x-rays, they just have your body vibrate and&nbsp;they&nbsp;record the vibration so they can analyze any organ in your body&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"798\" height=\"390\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-52.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4321\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-52.png 798w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-52-300x147.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-52-768x375.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 798px) 100vw, 798px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Not only organs of the body, but parts of the organs of the body and your veins and whatever, they can&nbsp;[Laughs]&nbsp;analyze those with vibration.&nbsp;And then,&nbsp;when they find out where the weak parts of your body, then&nbsp;they put the right vibration back in there to help cure.&nbsp;So, of&nbsp;course, this is&nbsp;not a real&nbsp;strange to some people who are into alternative medicine.&nbsp;So&nbsp;we see that there are many healings like Reiki and chronic healing, which&nbsp;basically put&nbsp;some vibration into your body to cure the organs.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"895\" height=\"451\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-53.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4322\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-53.png 895w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-53-300x151.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-53-768x387.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 895px) 100vw, 895px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So materially speaking, your body is&nbsp;vibration&nbsp;and it senses the vibration.&nbsp;That&#8217;s&nbsp;the conclusion&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;We know that the brain is full of brain waves.&nbsp;So&nbsp;brain&nbsp;wave&nbsp;is&nbsp;also a vibration. And&nbsp;they&#8217;ve&nbsp;analyzed it,&nbsp;different types&nbsp;of waves&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So&nbsp;the beta state,&nbsp;that&#8217;s&nbsp;your waking state.&nbsp;And then we have these other states, which we can say are your sleep states&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;And you have to have all these states in your brain, otherwise your brain isn&#8217;t operating properly.&nbsp;And&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;all&nbsp;frequency,&nbsp;we see that the beta state is more&nbsp;frequency&nbsp;and then we get&nbsp;less and less&nbsp;frequency as we go to these more subtle waves&nbsp;in the brain.&nbsp;And there we see the second one, the alpha wave. This is quite important&nbsp;because this is the&nbsp;one that is used in meditation.&nbsp;So&nbsp;if people can get into the alpha state, they can meditate nicely. And many doctors nowadays, they also say if you can get into the alpha state, you can also put messages in there to cure your body [Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"484\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-54.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4323\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-54.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-54-300x161.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-54-768x413.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So anyway,&nbsp;brain&nbsp;is full of these vibrations.&nbsp;Apart from these different frequencies in your waking state, your thoughts are made up of vibrations also. And with the use of computers nowadays,&nbsp;they&#8217;ve&nbsp;been able to translate your brainwaves, so they know what&nbsp;you&#8217;re&nbsp;thinking&nbsp;[Laughs]. Of course, we also have the opposite.&nbsp;The computer can send thought waves into your brain and make you&nbsp;think&nbsp;things&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So&nbsp;in other words, some&nbsp;computer&nbsp;could control your thoughts&nbsp;[Laughs]. So,&nbsp;we see this in many science&nbsp;and&nbsp;fiction movies, but it&#8217;s not actually&nbsp;fiction,&nbsp;it&#8217;s actually happening in this world.&nbsp;They have the techniques to make you&nbsp;think&nbsp;things&nbsp;[Laughs]. We often hear also certain yogis or what people&nbsp;doing black magic&nbsp;can also control your thoughts&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"505\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-55.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4324\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-55.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-55-300x168.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-55-768x430.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Yeah, okay, so&nbsp;that&#8217;s&nbsp;our body and our brains are full of vibrations, etc.&nbsp;Earth also is vibrating.&nbsp;There&#8217;s&nbsp;a certain vibration of the Earth, 7.83 hertz. This is the Schumann resonance, and&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;scientifically recorded.&nbsp;And interestingly enough, this is the same frequency as your alpha wave frequency in your brain.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in other words, when&nbsp;you&#8217;re&nbsp;in a very meditative state,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;actually&nbsp;you&#8217;re&nbsp;resonating with the Earth vibration.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in other words, the Earth and its natural state of vibration&nbsp;is&nbsp;conducive to meditative&nbsp;state, curing the body, etc.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"438\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-43.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4305\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-43.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-43-300x146.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-43-768x373.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Unfortunately, in the modern world, we also see that we have many scientific inventions and things like that, which&nbsp;kind of interfere&nbsp;with the natural vibration of the Earth. We have all sorts of electrical waves, we have all these cell phone towers,&nbsp;we&#8217;ve&nbsp;got these satellites up in space, putting vibrations everywhere. This also interferes with the natural vibration of the Earth.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"414\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-56.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4325\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-56.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-56-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-56-768x353.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Actually, in&nbsp;ancient times, even though we say that they were very primitive people, they were also&nbsp;very sensitive&nbsp;to the vibration of the Earth. At certain places around the Earth, they built these huge monuments. Even before they had tools and things, they were building these huge monuments&nbsp;at&nbsp;certain places.&nbsp;So&nbsp;these places were very sacred. So why were they&nbsp;sacred? Because they could sense that at these places, we have this natural vibration of the Earth. We also see in&nbsp;yoga, generally&nbsp;not&nbsp;there&nbsp;in the cities.&nbsp;So&nbsp;they go up to the forest, or they go to the&nbsp;Himalayas&nbsp;[Laughs]. And why? Because the cities are for all the wrong vibrations&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;It&#8217;s&nbsp;not conducive&nbsp;for&nbsp;meditation.&nbsp;And even in our devotional literature, like&nbsp;Nectar of Devotion,&nbsp;Rupa Goswami&nbsp;recommends,&nbsp;you want to perform&nbsp;bhakti,&nbsp;you go to a sacred place like&nbsp;Vrindavan&nbsp;&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"618\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-57.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4326\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-57.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-57-300x206.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-57-768x527.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Okay, so apart from the Earth, and apart from our body, and our brain, etc., all vibrating,&nbsp;the human being is&nbsp;very attracted to vibration, and therefore, even in ancient societies, they had music. Of course, any sound is a vibration.&nbsp;But music is very&nbsp;specific&nbsp;vibrations in relation to other vibrations, which make notes.&nbsp;So&nbsp;all these frequencies have mathematical relationships with each other. Notes, so we have the notes of the scale, and&nbsp;they&#8217;re&nbsp;mathematically related according to vibration.&nbsp;And if you&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;get the right vibration, then&nbsp;they&#8217;ll&nbsp;say, ah,&nbsp;you&#8217;re&nbsp;not singing properly.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"526\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-58.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4327\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-58.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-58-300x175.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-58-768x448.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So interestingly enough, these vibrations also resonate with your chakras.&nbsp;In the body, we have subtle energy, or subtle energy centers called the chakras. These are very well known in yoga. We cannot see them, but the yogis can see them [Laughs]. And these chakras are also vibrating at different frequencies.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"619\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-59.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4328\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-59.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-59-300x206.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-59-768x528.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And as we ascend from one chakra to the other, the frequency has become&nbsp;more and more&nbsp;subtle [Laughs].&nbsp;Yeah, so those are the basic frequencies of the chakras, and&nbsp;they&#8217;re&nbsp;also associated with certain emotions.&nbsp;They&#8217;re&nbsp;also associated with certain organs of your body.&nbsp;For instance,&nbsp;we&#8217;ll&nbsp;have the fourth chakra, which is your heart chakra. So, on one level,&nbsp;if it is not resonating&nbsp;or&nbsp;vibrating, you&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;have good relationships with people. But it also is related to your physical heart, and if&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;not vibrating properly, your heart&#8217;s&nbsp;gonna&nbsp;have problems [Laughs].&nbsp;So&nbsp;if we play the right vibration for the right chakra, we can get your chakra vibrating at the right rate, then we can cure your emotions and cure your heart problems [Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"405\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-60.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4329\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-60.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-60-300x135.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-60-768x345.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;this is&nbsp;using music to also cure the body, based on vibration.&nbsp;So&nbsp;this is an area which can be investigated in the future. But there are some people in alternative medicine using tones to adjust your chakras.&nbsp;When we take&nbsp;the musical&nbsp;notes and then we combine&nbsp;it&nbsp;in certain ways with rhythm, we get music.&nbsp;So&nbsp;scientists have found that music also has profound effects on living entities.&nbsp;Plants don&#8217;t have nervous systems, they don&#8217;t have ears, they don&#8217;t have brains.&nbsp;But they like certain types of music, and they&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;like other&nbsp;[Laughs]&nbsp;types of music&nbsp;[Laughs]. So,&nbsp;if&nbsp;they&nbsp;get some nice gentle classical music or ragas, they like it, which means they grow very nicely.&nbsp;And if&nbsp;they&nbsp;get very loud, dissonant music, then the plants&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;like&nbsp;it,&nbsp;they&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;grow.&nbsp;So logically speaking, if plants somehow detect different types of music and it affects their growth, etc., it should have an effect on animals also.&nbsp;So&nbsp;they do experiments on animals, and true, same thing, same effect.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"438\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-61.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4330\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-61.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-61-300x146.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-61-768x373.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;in&nbsp;Tokyo&nbsp;University, they got little mice&nbsp;[Laughs], and they played&nbsp;different types&nbsp;of music to them, and they found, yes, it affects the mice&nbsp;[Laughs]. And&nbsp;so&nbsp;if you play&nbsp;mozart&nbsp;music or classical music, if they have some problem, they get healed quickly. And if you play some loud dissonant music, they&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;heal.&nbsp;And they also found that the music affected their intelligence, their IQ. So simply by&nbsp;different types&nbsp;of music, you could affect the intelligence of the mice&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"487\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-62.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4331\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-62.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-62-300x162.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-62-768x415.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;if you play all this loud, dissonant music,&nbsp;IQ&nbsp;went&nbsp;down.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in other words, if your children are struggling in school, better keep all the bad [Laughs] music away from them, give them some classical music [Laughs]&nbsp;maybe their&nbsp;IQ is&nbsp;gonna&nbsp;improve [Laughs]. And they also found, as they exposed the mice to this loud music continuously for like two weeks, the mice became completely unmanageable, and they began killing each other.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in other words, this music had&nbsp;a very strong&nbsp;influence on mice.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"432\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-63.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4332\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-63.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-63-300x144.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-63-768x368.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;human beings, of course, have more advanced brains, and we will expect that, again, music would affect them in different ways&nbsp;and that was true. They found that&nbsp;the soft, gentle music was good for healing.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"526\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-64.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4333\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-64.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-64-300x175.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-64-768x448.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And the loud music increased the cortisol hormone in your body, and this made healing more, more difficult. So fast music produces stress. And this, of course, is useful. It makes you&nbsp;very excited. And therefore, in&nbsp;military, they have a lot of marching bands and all this sort of stuff. In sports, they have a lot of this loud music to get everybody&nbsp;excited [Laughs]. However, if this is done constantly to&nbsp;the human being, we get all the stress, we get all this cortisol, it starts destroying the body.&nbsp;So&nbsp;if you have your children all stuck to the earphones and having all this loud music day and night, you be&nbsp;very careful&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;They&#8217;re&nbsp;going to destroy their minds and their bodies.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"502\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-65.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4334\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-65.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-65-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-65-768x428.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So,&nbsp;some countries have also used sound as a weapon. And with that sound weapon, they can make people panic, they can make them run away, they can paralyze people, make you sick. There was&nbsp;a&nbsp;article in the newspaper, I mean, half a year ago, there was demonstrations in Serbia.&nbsp;They&nbsp;didn&#8217;t&nbsp;like the government.&nbsp;Then suddenly, in the middle of&nbsp;demonstration, everybody panicked and ran away&nbsp;[Laughs]. So many bystanders were saying they were using a sound weapon&nbsp;[Laughs], because there was no, you know, no&nbsp;guns or anything, but the people&nbsp;panicked&nbsp;and they all ran away&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"486\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-66.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4335\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-66.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-66-300x162.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-66-768x414.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;in&nbsp;Bhagavad Gita,&nbsp;we have a description of&nbsp;gunas, three modes of existence, sattva,&nbsp;rajas&nbsp;and tamas. And everything in the material world can be classified into these groups. And the result of tamasic things is,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;destructive.&nbsp;Rajas&nbsp;produce&nbsp;passion. And sattva is healing.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in&nbsp;Bhagavad Gita, everything begins to be classified according to these gunas&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"475\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-67.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4336\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-67.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-67-300x158.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-67-768x405.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;we can classify&nbsp;the music.&nbsp;The healing&nbsp;music is&nbsp;the sattvic&nbsp;music. The destructive music is&nbsp;the tamasic&nbsp;music [Laughs]. And similarly, for foods, the foods which heal and sustain your body, vegetarian foods, they are sattvic.&nbsp;And then the tamasic would be&nbsp;animal.&nbsp;And of course, we have all these artificial foods, chemical foods, preservatives,&nbsp;all of&nbsp;this stuff, very, very destructive to your body.&nbsp;So&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;all tamasic [Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"556\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-68.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4337\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-68.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-68-300x185.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-68-768x474.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Okay, so sound we think&nbsp;of&nbsp;course,&nbsp;is a vibration, but in the modern world,&nbsp;they&#8217;ve&nbsp;also discovered that sound is a form.&nbsp;So&nbsp;they have a little instrument like&nbsp;this&nbsp;and they put particles of sand on a vibrating plate, and it forms into patterns.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"516\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-69.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-69.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-69-300x172.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-69-768x440.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So&nbsp;each note of the scale has a specific pattern to go with it as well. So,&nbsp;sound is not only for the ear, but it also has a visual form as well.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in other words,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;a little more complex than we think it is&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"420\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-70.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4339\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-70.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-70-300x140.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-70-768x358.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Yeah, okay, so,&nbsp;sound&nbsp;has a form. And in India, of course, a mantra is the sound. But they also gave&nbsp;sound&nbsp;or the mantra a form.&nbsp;That&#8217;s&nbsp;called the yantra.&nbsp;So&nbsp;all the famous mantras also have&nbsp;yantras,&nbsp;forms to go with them. So, in this way, again, sound is not just sound, but it also has form [Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"499\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-71.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4340\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-71.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-71-300x166.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-71-768x425.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So,&nbsp;in India, they have a musical theory called raga.&nbsp;So&nbsp;they have&nbsp;the notes&nbsp;of&nbsp;the scale.&nbsp;And you choose a certain five, six, or seven&nbsp;notes,&nbsp;this becomes the raga.&nbsp;But you have to combine those notes&nbsp;in a certain&nbsp;way to get the&nbsp;right effect.&nbsp;So&nbsp;for&nbsp;each raga&nbsp;then, they give you a form.&nbsp;So&nbsp;this form is actually a person.&nbsp;Maybe&nbsp;Vishnu&nbsp;[Laughs]. Or&nbsp;maybe Krishna. May be some devata.&nbsp;They may be&nbsp;black or white or yellow or red&nbsp;or green,&nbsp;different colors&nbsp;[Laughs]. They may have&nbsp;two hands&nbsp;or four arms or six arms or eight arms or whatever. And&nbsp;they&#8217;re&nbsp;doing&nbsp;different types&nbsp;of&nbsp;activities.&nbsp;So&nbsp;when you learn the notes of the raga, you&nbsp;have to&nbsp;meditate on this&nbsp;particular form&nbsp;as well.&nbsp;So&nbsp;if you are able to sing&nbsp;or play those notes&nbsp;properly, then the form should manifest. So again, we see that the form and sound are related together.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"514\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-72.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4341\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-72.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-72-300x171.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-72-768x438.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;another&nbsp;aspect of sound is&nbsp;formation&nbsp;of words. In the modern world, we just say sound, of course, is air molecules vibrating and going into your ear&nbsp;[Laughs]. And certain combinations of vibration&nbsp;make words, and then we give that&nbsp;a meaning.&nbsp;And the word has been very&nbsp;important,&nbsp;it&nbsp;gives us knowledge. They did experiments on chimpanzees&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So&nbsp;they raised a chimpanzee from birth with human beings, and they talked to the chimpanzee and tried to get him to speak&nbsp;[Laughs]. But the maximum&nbsp;words&nbsp;is&nbsp;like 25 words, that was the maximum.&nbsp;It&#8217;s&nbsp;like a two-year-old, three-year-old&nbsp;[Laughs],&nbsp;maybe two-year-old,&nbsp;5, 10 words, 15 words like that. But adult human beings will have thousands and thousands of words. And&nbsp;we&#8217;ll&nbsp;see that more advanced civilizations have more words and complex combinations of words, and therefore they produce science and art&nbsp;etc.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"481\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-73.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4342\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-73.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-73-300x160.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-73-768x410.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">However, in&nbsp;the Vedic&nbsp;literature,&nbsp;there&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;different&nbsp;concept&nbsp;of words.&nbsp;Actually, the&nbsp;word for sound and word are the same in Sanskrit,&nbsp;<em>sabda&nbsp;<\/em>[Laughs]. And we use the word&nbsp;<em>sabda<\/em>,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;not&nbsp;an&nbsp;any random&nbsp;sound.&nbsp;It&#8217;s&nbsp;sound with a meaning to it. And that sound does not go through&nbsp;air.&nbsp;It goes through ether,&nbsp;<em>akash<\/em>. So,&nbsp;it is a little more subtle than our modern concept of sound&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"508\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-74.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4343\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-74.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-74-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-74-768x433.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And these words are very intimately associated with&nbsp;Supreme&nbsp;Lord and spiritual life.&nbsp;So&nbsp;we see that&nbsp;Hayagriva&nbsp;the horse avatar, breathes, and out of&nbsp;His&nbsp;breathing comes all the Vedas.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"447\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-75.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4344\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-75.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-75-300x149.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-75-768x381.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">We see the word&nbsp;<em>\u2018Om\u2019<\/em>&nbsp;is celebrated throughout the Vedas.&nbsp;So&nbsp;this is sound,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;also a symbol of&nbsp;word.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"456\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-76.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4345\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-76.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-76-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-76-768x389.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And it actually represents Vishnu.&nbsp;It is one simple sound, but it&nbsp;contains&nbsp;all the sounds of the Sanskrit alphabet. And from that one sound, expands&nbsp;all&nbsp;the sounds, the syllables, and then the whole Vedas expands from one simple syllable. And&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;not&nbsp;material&nbsp;sound.&nbsp;It&#8217;s&nbsp;spiritual&nbsp;sound [Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"735\" height=\"570\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4262\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-1.png 735w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-1-300x233.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;in other words, the Vedas recognize sound, but&nbsp;they&#8217;re&nbsp;talking about spiritual sound, non-different from the Supreme Lord. So,&nbsp;the spiritual sound permeates the spiritual world, but it also&nbsp;enters into&nbsp;and permeates the material world.&nbsp;So&nbsp;in other words, the syllable&nbsp;Om&nbsp;pervades all the material elements like earth, water, fire, air, ether,&nbsp;etc&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"484\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-78.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4347\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-78.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-78-300x161.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-78-768x413.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Okay, so,&nbsp;the Vedas also say that&nbsp;\u2018<em>Om\u2019<\/em>&nbsp;is the source, and of course the Supreme Lord&nbsp;is the source of material creation.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"430\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-79.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4348\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-79.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-79-300x143.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-79-768x367.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">In Brahma Samhita it explains that Brahma,&nbsp;who&#8217;s&nbsp;trying to create the universe, could not do so, so he meditates on Supreme Lord. Brahma&nbsp;hears the sound of&nbsp;Krishna&#8217;s flute, which becomes the Gayatri mantra, which comes from&nbsp;<em>\u2018Om\u2019<\/em>&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-80.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4349\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-80.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-80-300x111.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-80-768x285.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And then by uttering this Gayatri mantra, Brahma was able to create the universe.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"807\" height=\"343\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-81.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-81.png 807w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-81-300x128.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-81-768x326.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 807px) 100vw, 807px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">In other words, through that sound, he got the power&nbsp;of creating&nbsp;this universe.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"280\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-82.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4351\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-82.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-82-300x93.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-82-768x239.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Even in modern science, some scientists are saying that sound was also integral in the creation of the universe after the Big Bang [Laughs]. Of course, even Big Bang is controversial, because some scientists&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;agree there was a Big Bang [Laughs]. And of course, in Vedic literature, we find that creation is&nbsp;nothing,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;a repeated attempt [Laughs]. Creation, destruction,&nbsp;creation, destruction, it goes on forever [Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"364\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-83.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4352\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-83.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-83-300x121.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-83-768x310.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So,&nbsp;anyway, we are interested in spiritual&nbsp;sound. And we call this mantra. The literal meaning of&nbsp;mantra&nbsp;is,&nbsp;<em>man<\/em>&nbsp;stands for&nbsp;<em>manas<\/em>, which means mind,&nbsp;<em>tra<\/em>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<em>trayate<\/em>, to deliver.&nbsp;So,&nbsp;mantra is&nbsp;a&nbsp;specific sound, spiritual sound, which takes the mind away from&nbsp;material&nbsp;world, takes you to the spiritual world.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"474\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-84.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4353\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-84.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-84-300x158.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-84-768x404.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So, the mantra is considered to be&nbsp;same&nbsp;as&nbsp;Supreme&nbsp;Lord, not different. And even if Lord is not here as avatar, we cannot see Him, still we have the mantra. &nbsp;So&nbsp;through the mantra, we can access the Supreme Lord. Of course, the question will arise, well, how can spiritual sound appear in the material world, and how can we hear it if we have only material ears?&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"415\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-85.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4354\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-85.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-85-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-85-768x354.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;this is also explained in the scriptures. That spiritual sound is called&nbsp;para.&nbsp;But it becomes gradually accessible to us, first accessible to our mind. This is called the&nbsp;pasyanti&nbsp;level. And then when we begin to think about it with our intellect&nbsp;and&nbsp;analyze the&nbsp;sound means&nbsp;that or whatever,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;called&nbsp;madhyama.&nbsp;And then when we can pronounce the actual word with our vocal cords, and then somebody can hear it,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;called&nbsp;vaikhari. And it also goes through the different chakras&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;Yeah.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"448\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4263\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2-300x149.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2-768x382.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So anyway, the sound is originally spiritual, and then it becomes accessible to our mind, intelligence, and our voice, and our ear, but it&nbsp;remains&nbsp;spiritual.&nbsp;So&nbsp;we can hear&nbsp;with our material ear, we can say with our material vocal cords, but&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;still spiritual.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"501\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4264\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3-768x427.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Okay, so, that mantra comes from the spiritual world, and gradually&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;accessible to us,&nbsp;so we can say it and hear it, but still, it&nbsp;maintains&nbsp;its spiritual quality, and then we become spiritualized.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"541\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4265\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4-768x461.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So&nbsp;this para, spiritual side&nbsp;remains, even though&nbsp;we&#8217;re&nbsp;operating&nbsp;on this level and saying it&nbsp;and hearing it [Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"508\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-86.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4355\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-86.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-86-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-86-768x433.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Okay, so that mantra, of course, is spiritual, but it also has material effects. Now,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;difficult for us to measure spiritual&nbsp;effects, because&nbsp;we&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;have spiritual scientific instruments&nbsp;[Laughs]. But we can measure material effects.&nbsp;So, different scientists have studied, you know, chanting Gayatri mantra and Sanskrit mantras and seeing the effect on your DNA, and they say, yes, it has some positive effect.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"421\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-87.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4356\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-87.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-87-300x140.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-87-768x359.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">About 10 years ago, when studying chromosomes, then one scientist discovered what are called telomeres.&nbsp;So&nbsp;these are these little tips on your chromosomes here.&nbsp;So&nbsp;these are important, because by the size of the telomeres, they can measure your health. If you have long telomeres, then&nbsp;you&#8217;re&nbsp;in good health, and you can repair your body, and you&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;have diseases. Now, normally, as people get older, those telomeres get smaller and smaller, and&nbsp;consequently, you start losing your health as you get older, get more sickness.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"487\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-88.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4357\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-88.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-88-300x162.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-88-768x415.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So, therefore, by analyzing your telomeres, we can measure your health and how fast you&nbsp;are&nbsp;aging&nbsp;[Laughs]. So here we see the old person with the short telomeres&nbsp;[Laughs], and the younger person with the bigger telomeres&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;Yeah, so, then, the whole object of science would be to&nbsp;see,&nbsp;how we can, when your telomeres start getting smaller, how to make them bigger again.&nbsp;And this was, by looking at your telomeres,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;very&nbsp;objective way of seeing if this&nbsp;particular diet&nbsp;had&nbsp;a good effect.&nbsp;So&nbsp;they tried&nbsp;vegetarian&nbsp;diet,&nbsp;okay,&nbsp;you get&nbsp;4%&nbsp;increase in your telomeres. They tried&nbsp;exercise,&nbsp;walking&nbsp;every day for half an hour.&nbsp;And you could increase your telomeres by 5%. They tried yoga,&nbsp;okay,&nbsp;5%. They tried some simple meditation techniques,&nbsp;okay,&nbsp;5%.&nbsp;They tried soft music,&nbsp;again,&nbsp;you get about 5%&nbsp;[Laughs]. They tried weekly&nbsp;meetings,&nbsp;people get together, talk together, socialize a little bit, and again, 5%. And then they tried&nbsp;Kirtan,&nbsp;and they got&nbsp;43% increase&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;Of course,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;a nice combination, because we have music, we have mantra, which is spiritual, vegetarian food, we have people coming&nbsp;together, we have music, everything. So, they were very&nbsp;good&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So, this is just a physical effect.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"462\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-89.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-89.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-89-300x154.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-89-768x394.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And of course, you can measure the effects on your mind also and they found, yes, it does affect the mind, you sleep better,&nbsp;etc, you know, you breathe better, etc.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"409\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-90.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4359\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-90.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-90-300x136.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-90-768x349.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Unfortunately, we cannot measure&nbsp;spiritual&nbsp;effect&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So, we have to go by scripture.&nbsp;So, of course, the most significant effect of mantra is a spiritual effect&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;But the scriptures tell us that the mantra, that sound, and the form of the&nbsp;Lord&nbsp;are non-different. So, by chanting the mantra, you should realize the form of the Lord. The sound&nbsp;Krishna&nbsp;and&nbsp;Krishna&nbsp;are non-different.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"571\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-91.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-91.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-91-300x190.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-91-768x487.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Of course, we chant&nbsp;<em>Hare Krishna&nbsp;<\/em>and therefore we realize&nbsp;Radha&nbsp;and&nbsp;Krishna. So,&nbsp;why,&nbsp;what&#8217;s&nbsp;the significance of chanting&nbsp;Krishna? Of course,&nbsp;Krishna&nbsp;is&nbsp;form&nbsp;of the Supreme Lord.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"442\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-92.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4361\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-92.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-92-300x147.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-92-768x377.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">But of all the names of the Lord, the name&nbsp;Krishna&nbsp;is considered to be the number one name.&nbsp;But why is it number one&nbsp;[Laughs]? So, that word has been analyzed. So,&nbsp;Krishna&nbsp;has two syllables,&nbsp;\u2018<em>Krish\u2019<\/em>&nbsp;and&nbsp;\u2018n<em>a\u2019<\/em>.&nbsp;So, the scriptures tell us that&nbsp;\u2018Krish\u2019&nbsp;means He is the source of everything, spiritually and materially.&nbsp;And&nbsp;\u2018n<em>a\u2019<\/em>&nbsp;means He is the source of all&nbsp;bliss. And of course, everybody wants to be blissful eternally. So, if you realize&nbsp;Krishna, you get eternal bliss.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"517\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-93.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-93.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-93-300x172.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-93-768x441.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">We also say Hare Rama. What does&nbsp;<em>\u2018Rama\u2019<\/em>&nbsp;mean? So, Rama means the person&nbsp;who gives&nbsp;bliss. And we chant the name&nbsp;<em>Hare<\/em>,&nbsp;this&nbsp;represents&nbsp;Radha, who is Hladini shakti, the very embodiment of all bliss. So, by chanting Hare Krishna, we realize Radha and Krishna. How is it significant? We get the highest bliss.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"511\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-94.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4363\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-94.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-94-300x170.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-94-768x436.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, therefore, mantra is sound, but it is&nbsp;spiritual&nbsp;sound.&nbsp;And we can study its physical effects or its mental effects, that&nbsp;we&nbsp;can see that.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"523\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4266\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7-300x174.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7-768x446.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But ultimately, we&nbsp;are interested in the spiritual effect on the&nbsp;atma.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"330\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4261\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-300x110.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-768x281.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So, through the mantra, we can get&nbsp;highest&nbsp;eternal spiritual bliss. We can get out of the material world and get into the spiritual world.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"901\" height=\"555\" src=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-95.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4364\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-95.png 901w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-95-300x185.png 300w, https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-95-768x473.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Okay,&nbsp;Hare Krishna!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Q &amp; A:<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\"><strong>1.) Maharaj, as you&nbsp;explained&nbsp;every mantra has a yantra and a form, so how does Hare Krishna&nbsp;Maha&nbsp;mantra look like?<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So, though mantras have yantras to them, when we say&nbsp;Hare Krishna&nbsp;mantra,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;a little bit different.&nbsp;It&#8217;s&nbsp;mantra definitely, but&nbsp;a&nbsp;little different&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So&nbsp;to distinguish, we call it&nbsp;Nama.&nbsp;So, we&nbsp;say&nbsp;Nama&nbsp;Sankirtan. So, though mantras have the&nbsp;Name&nbsp;of the Lord in them, Nama is just&nbsp;Name&nbsp;of the Lord. So, for the mantras, there are all sorts of rules you&nbsp;have to&nbsp;follow for those mantras to make them effective.&nbsp;And to help you concentrate, you have the yantras. However, when we just have the&nbsp;Name, all&nbsp;that&#8217;s&nbsp;not necessary. So, there&#8217;s&nbsp;minimum&nbsp;rules to follow.&nbsp;And through the&nbsp;Name,&nbsp;we can directly realize&nbsp;form&nbsp;of Krishna.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\"><strong>Devotee:<\/strong>&nbsp;Thank&nbsp;you&nbsp;Maharaj.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\"><strong>2.)&nbsp;Maharaj, in&nbsp;the&nbsp;abrahmanic&nbsp;culture, in Judaism, Christianity, and Islam, we see a common word&nbsp;<\/strong><strong><em>amen<\/em><\/strong><strong>. Is it any way connected to&nbsp;<\/strong><strong><em>OM<\/em><\/strong>?&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">[Laughs]&nbsp;I&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;know,&nbsp;from the scholar&#8217;s point of view, you know, how they derive the words and where it comes from, etc. But obviously, it&nbsp;looks like it&#8217;s&nbsp;similar.&nbsp;The word&nbsp;Om&nbsp;itself analyzes&nbsp;ah,&nbsp;uh&nbsp;and um&nbsp;which means&nbsp;all of&nbsp;the syllables, the vowels, all the vowels&nbsp;[Laughs], plus the nasal sound. So, it&nbsp;represents&nbsp;all&nbsp;sound. And then it&nbsp;represents&nbsp;Vishnu&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So, I suppose, even in Christianity&nbsp;if they use that word,&nbsp;it ultimately,&nbsp;amen&nbsp;is equivalent with God.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\"><strong>3.)&nbsp;Maharaj another question is, we see novel writers, 50 years back, 70 years back, they wrote science fiction novels which is now happening we see. Are they coming from different worlds&nbsp;to just&nbsp;guide us?<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So difficult to&nbsp;say&nbsp;about these authors, but some scientists, like Nikola Tesla, for instance, it looks like he got some&nbsp;[Laughs], he&nbsp;was a little eccentric character, and he would seem to be getting information from somewhere else&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;And even&nbsp;there&#8217;s&nbsp;a famous mathematician,&nbsp;Ramanujan&nbsp;in India.&nbsp;Very famous, he was just like a clerk&nbsp;[Laughs]&nbsp;working for the British. But somehow, he was a very, very profound mathematician, and he would have visions of&nbsp;Narasimha Dev&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Of course, where does all knowledge come from? This is a big question. And many&nbsp;scientists, they&nbsp;also&nbsp;don&#8217;t&nbsp;know where they got their theory from. Somehow, it came in their&nbsp;head&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So, now, of course, modern rational theory would just think that&nbsp;one, you know,&nbsp;civilization leads to another, and they borrow their ideas, and then they expand on that. So, we have&nbsp;gradual&nbsp;evolution of things, and we get discoveries that way.&nbsp;That&#8217;s&nbsp;one way of thinking.&nbsp;But then the other way is,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;coming from somewhere else&nbsp;[Laughs]. And that, of course, is how knowledge is explained in the Vedas. Its origin is ultimately&nbsp;Supreme&nbsp;Lord, material&nbsp;knowledge&nbsp;and spiritual knowledge.&nbsp;And at certain periods,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;revealed. Sometimes, it gets destroyed&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\"><strong>4.) Maharaj ji,&nbsp;I have a small question&nbsp;here. Like, today, on social media&nbsp;what we have,&nbsp;you can see there is a positive and a negative impact. So, what do you see from&nbsp;the&nbsp;spiritual point of view? What is the impact on&nbsp;the society?<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">So, things in the material&nbsp;world, you&nbsp;can have positive aspects and negative aspects. Just like food&nbsp;could&nbsp;be positive or negative&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;Medicine&nbsp;could&nbsp;be positive or negative&nbsp;[Laughs]. So,&nbsp;internet&nbsp;could&nbsp;be positive or negative&nbsp;[Laughs]. We can use it constructively,&nbsp;very good. But it can also be used or manipulated in&nbsp;other&nbsp;way, and it becomes completely useless and&nbsp;maybe&nbsp;[Laughs]&nbsp;negative. And we cannot sacrifice our consciousness for mechanical devices.&nbsp;We cannot replace our intellect&nbsp;by&nbsp;AI&nbsp;[Laughs]. We give up thinking and let AI do everything for us, and then we&nbsp;can&#8217;t&nbsp;think anymore. So, that&#8217;s&nbsp;useless&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\"><strong>5.) So,&nbsp;Maharaj, when we hear the mantra from&nbsp;youtube&nbsp;or some machine, does that have an effect?<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Oh, interesting&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;So, mantras like&nbsp;you know,&nbsp;Gayatri mantra and Vedic mantras are&nbsp;very specific, so they will lose a lot of their power.&nbsp;Now,&nbsp;Name&nbsp;of the&nbsp;Lord, of course, is more powerful and whether you chant it with good&nbsp;conscious, bad&nbsp;conscious, or whatever&nbsp;[Laughs]&nbsp;it has some effect&nbsp;[Laughs]. At the same time, in different conditions, it will be strong or&nbsp;maybe weak.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">And we know that,&nbsp;when we hear things over with microphones or with internet or whatever,&nbsp;actually it&nbsp;is not the original sound&nbsp;[Laughs].&nbsp;It is some mechanical thing which is vibrating and giving us some sound which we can recognize. So, that is why, originally,&nbsp;Vedic&nbsp;knowledge was transmitted personally from one person to another. So, there is always&nbsp;an extra&nbsp;energy&nbsp;[Laughs]&nbsp;when it is heard directly.&nbsp;And then of course,&nbsp;it&#8217;s&nbsp;also&nbsp;people&nbsp;realize that. So, you can always&nbsp;hear&nbsp;music on it or buy some recording or mp3 and stick it in your ear.&nbsp;But if that person comes personally and you&nbsp;get&nbsp;a direct&nbsp;contact&nbsp;of&nbsp;that person, then you get much more excited&nbsp;[Laughs]. So, there is some other energy present when the person is personally present.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\">Hare Krsna !&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-justify has-text-align-justify\"><strong>Devotees:&nbsp;<\/strong>Thank you very&nbsp;much Maharaj&nbsp;for your wonderful class.<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong>HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj ki jai!!! Srila&nbsp;Prabhupada&nbsp;ki jai!!!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Seminar on\u00a0Mysteries of Sound\u00a0| HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj | ISKCON Japan | November 9,\u00a02025\u00a0|\u00a0 Hare&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;K\u1e5b\u1e63\u1e47a&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;&nbsp; Hare&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;R\u0101ma&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;Hare&nbsp;&nbsp; Jaya&nbsp;Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;Jaya&nbsp;Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;Jaya&nbsp;Prabhup\u0101da&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj:&nbsp;&nbsp; So, in Lord Caitanya&#8217;s movement, Nama\u00a0Sankirtan\u00a0is considered the main process for spiritual advancement. And many people will question why this sound is so important? If we examine\u00a0the Vedic\u00a0literature,\u00a0we&#8217;ll\u00a0see that sound is\u00a0very important.\u00a0Apart from\u00a0what&#8217;s\u00a0stated\u00a0in [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-4260","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4260","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4260"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4260\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4381,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4260\/revisions\/4381"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4260"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}